org.universAAL.middleware.managers.configuration.core.impl.secondaryManagers

Class PendingRequestsManager

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.universAAL.middleware.managers.configuration.core.impl.secondaryManagers.PendingRequestsManager

  • public class PendingRequestsManager
extends Object
    Manage the Requests, waiting for responses. Specifically for remote configuration editors, that need to be created when the response arrives, and then added to the ConfigurationEditor.ConfigurableEntityManager.
    Author:
    amedrano
